            <thetext>Currently, we have three levels of qx.disposerDebugLevel 

0: no warnings at all
1: display warnings for every not disposed object
&gt;1: Display warnings for every not disposed object and show a message which object were disposed

Sometimes it could be helpful to split up the warnings in qooxdoo objects and non qooxdoo objects. Introducing a new level only for qooxdoo objects could help:

0: no warnings at all
1: display warnings for every not disposed qooxdoo object
2: display warnings for every not disposed object
&gt;2: Display warnings for every not disposed object and show a message which object were disposed</thetext>
